            <div class="tool-best-for"><strong>Best for:</strong> Small business operators that want SEO articles shipped without learning yet another platform.</div>
            <a href="/checkout/" class="tool-cta-btn">Start at $99/mo →</a>
          </div>
        </div>

        <div class="tool-card">
          <div class="tool-card-head">
            <div class="tool-rank">02</div>
            <div class="tool-card-info">
              <div class="tool-card-name">Search Atlas (OTTO SEO)</div>
              <div class="tool-card-tag">Best for full-stack SEO automation</div>
            </div>
            <div class="tool-card-price">
              <div class="price">$149<span style="font-size: 14px; color: var(--text-3);">/mo</span></div>
